title: TEF Canada: Section A Playbook
description: This document provides a strategic guide for successfully completing Section A of the TEF Canada Expression Orale exam. It contains a framework for structuring your conversation, key techniques to improve your performance, and a bank of ready-to-use questions for common topics.
